["SGITS provides innovative technological solutions that enable companies to adopt renewable energy with ease. Headquartered in Singapore, SGITS developed and operates Asia’s leading trading platform for Renewable Energy Certificates (RECs). We offer a one-stop ecosystem for RECs, supporting clients through the full REC lifecycle – asset registration, verification, marketplace and retirement.
A company committed to accelerate the global transition towards clean, green and renewable energy, We won the 2023 Emerging Enterprise Sustainability Award in Singapore.
You can find us here: https://redex.eco
Trách nhiệm công việc
As a Software Engineer, your key responsibilities include:
Developing innovative system management solutions and automation tools;
Self-managed, able to come up solution for technical problem, you are usually handle end-to-end for a feature or even a product;
Providing support for service operations also maintaining and enhancing the existing toolset;
Supporting automation initiatives in the production environment.
Kỹ năng & Chuyên môn
On Technical Side, we’re looking for a teammate with:
Have 3+ years of work experience in front-end development
Proficiency with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Typescript.
You may be familiar with state-of-the-art front end library or frameworks like ReactJs, VueJs;
Strong understanding of SASS/CSS, have experience writing UI library
Have knowledge about state management Context or libraries (e.g., Redux, Vuex);
Have experience writing unit tests is a plus;
Working experience with Git, Swagger, Figma…;
Focus on efficiency, user experience, and process improvement;
Experience with working with RDBMS such as SQL Server or MySQL will be an added bonus;
Experience in .NET or Nodejs is a plus;
Experience and Education:
Bachelor’s degree in computer programming, computer science, or a related field; We’d love to have you from 3 years of experience in software development for front-end, but absolutely open to talents;
Ability to work independently or with a group with good time management skills;
Demonstrate your problem-solving capabilities by effectively managing multiple projects concurrently, leveraging your strong analytical skills;
Self-motivated and an A team player; You’re expected to be comfortable working in a team, treating your peers with respect and dignity, willing to receive & give feedback to grow both personally and as an engineer. 
Ability to communicate effectively in English;
Phúc lợi dành cho bạn
Performance Management – Assess based on the Company's Performance Management Plan annually;
18 days off in a calendar year;
Performance review twice a year;
Premium Healthcare;
Great allowances (parking, birthday, happy hours, promotion…);
Outing/team-building activities (company trip, sports club…);
Monthly Gross Salary will be 100% for insurance and income tax purposes;
Probation Period: Two (2) Months with 100% monthly gross salary;
Other benefits as stated in Vietnamese Labor Law;
Training opportunity: both technical and soft skills to develop your career path;"]

['We are looking for a Senior or a Leader of Automation QC Team who have experience in working on different platforms to ensure the products are working properly. 
An Automation QC Senior or Leader will be responsible for  guiding our automation testing efforts, leading a team of skilled  engineers, and ensuring the efficient and effective testing of our  web applications and APIs. If you have a strong background in  automation testing with Java, API like Google API, Jira API,  Playwright, Selenium Web driver...; Networking, Robot framework,  we would like to hear from you.
Trách nhiệm công việc
Review requirements, specifications, and technical design documents to  provide timely and meaningful feedback;
Create detailed, comprehensive, and well-structured test plans and test cases;
Design, develop and execute automation scripts using open-source tools;
Develop and apply testing processes for new and existing products to meet  the day by day needs;
QC should able to perform Test Automation and setting up frameworks on  multiple application platforms like Web, Android, Ios and backend systems;
Create & manage bug reports and communicate with the team;
Investigate the causes of non-conforming software and train users to  implement solutions;
Track quality assurance metrics, like defect densities and open defect counts;
Oversee the development of automation test scripts for web applications using  Selenium with Java and JavaScript;
Utilize automation testing frameworks, tools, and best practices to drive team  efficiency and productivity;
Training & Mentoring of QC team members;
Report daily progress/issues to management and client representatives;
Other related duties as assigned.
Kỹ năng & Chuyên môn
Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or a related field;
At least 3 years of experience leading a team of 5 or more members in an automation testing role;
At least 5 years of experience with various mobile app/game and Web testing  for iOS and Android;
Have experience in web testing (Portal web, auto internet banking, OTP, ...);
Knowledge in API, performance and security testing;
Experience in writing clear, concise and comprehensive test plans and test  cases, test script;
Have a strong understanding of Non-Functional and Security testing;
Teamwork and cooperation skills, working well with a team;
Ability to handle pressure and meet strict deadlines;
Ability to use english in reading and writing test case, report bug, … speaking  is not compulsory;
Experience with game play, security logic, mobile game is a plus
Phúc lợi dành cho bạn
Competitive salary (based on skills and experience); 13th monthly salary and  performance bonus every year;
Review performance 2 times/ a year;
5-day working per week (From Monday to Friday);
PVI insurance;
Health Care Program;
Free coffee, snack and drinks; monthly Party;
Yearly Company trip, Team building activities;
Lunch Allowance;
Sport activities: Badminton, Gym, Yoga, Dancing;
Friendly work environment, no office politics.']

